swer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1006652/answer",,,,,"16","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","2018-11-13","Commonwealth: Press Freedom","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty's Government what discussions they have had with the Commonwealth Secretary-General about the Commonwealth Working Group on Media and Good Governance’s 2018 report on Commonwealth principles of freedom of expression and the role of the media in good governance.","false","Biography information for Lord Chidgey",,"Lord Chidgey","HL11432"
